Turrets:
 Concluded(or aproximate) {

  balista: A simple and small turret developed by crux, the beggining of something new. (crux, sharded)
, multi-balista: One sucessful attempt to upgrade the balista. (crux, sharded)
, cyber-balista: A powerfull laser shooter, a huge advance from the balista. (crux, sharded)

 Up coming:

  defensor: A tanky projectle destroyer, made to protect nearby blocks and destroy incoming strikes, developed by sharded. (sharded, crux)
, absorver: After crux saw the power of defensor, they decided to steal it's tech and improve further into their likings, a turret upgrade for phase walls. (crux, sharded)
, striker: Throughout the battle for who will dominate serpulo, sharded advanced further into offensive turrets, striking powerful attacks from far away, less effetive on units. (sharded)
, forbidden: Throughout the battle for who will dominate serpulo, crux advanced further into the ultimate defense, taken illegal by sharded, it's a nightmare for those who survived. (crux)
, traker(needs name ideas): This turret launches 7 bullets in a 360 angle that homes after little time, very fastly into nearby opponents, slow and pricy, but very effective. (crux)

